{"tid":268733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"給更生人士、前公務員重投社會","createTime":"2017-06-03T08:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T11:57:15.000Z","uid":40628,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9be84257ac421d800124a38c2c40c4ba2588195f","tid":268733,"uid":40628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T08:59:01.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://holland.pk/yuc2djst\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyuc2djst&h=4f562023&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府工作經驗成履歷負資產</span></span><br />\n<br />\n政府於2015至2016年度共有1,056名公務員辭職，當中有6成人為未過3年試用期便已「棄船圖生」。對於「跳船」數字，公務員工會聯合會總幹事梁籌庭直言今天的政府工「根本毫不吸引」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你在政府入面『歎』了這麼久，為什麼還要再出來工作？</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府工的經驗會是履歷「負資產」。「別人會想：你在政府入面『歎』了這麼久，為什麼還要再出來工作？在政府工作的經驗愈長，對方就愈會思疑你還有多少『戰鬥力』，如果是因為應付不到工作而重投商界，對方更會覺得你連政府工都應付不了，那如何去應付高競爭的商界環境呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"7a844ae3f4a895ec37635d61b96c60300673fbea","tid":268733,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T12:30:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee6116e5afd3eaaec6ce05b95294b6d80932e1c","tid":268733,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:32:52.000Z","msg":"更生人士好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要同前公務員比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f466fbfc1cfa420267d37d2609d1600ef20149b1","tid":268733,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T10:58:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>更生人士好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要同前公務員比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我地要盡量支持佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096353c48fa8578514bd8db598b3dd753f545e0a","tid":268733,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T11:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請支持公務員"},{"pid":"3b1b3f32a6f8f0fd0891bfd427e4558f7435ad4c","tid":268733,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T11:57:15.000Z","msg":"班所謂義士坐完監又真係好難重投社會既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}